getRelativeResource

public org.apache.wicket.Resource getRelativeResource(String relativePath)
Return a Resource accessed via a relative path from this Resource. Each Resource created for such queries will be remembered, and the same Resource will be returned again for a later query. This allows for the child Resources to do caching.
